data.description: Completely renovated 4 bedroom/2 bath home in Nottinghill Subdivision! Located 10 minutes south of Moody Air Force Base. Step into this functional split floor plan with upgrades throughout. Open concept kitchen, living, and dining rooms- perfect for entertaining. LVP flooring flows throughout main areas and bedrooms, tile in bathrooms- no carpet for easy maintenance. Kitchen features stainless steel appliances, island with seating, pantry, and plenty of counter space/cabinet storage w/ pull out drawers. Entire interior (ceilings, walls, trim, doors, cabinets) and exterior have just been repainted. All new light fixtures, blinds, door hardware, and plumbing fixtures. Primary bedroom includes his and hers closets, dual vanities, soaking tub, and walk in shower. Spare bedrooms are perfect for kids of all ages, a home office, or flex space. Granite countertops throughout. Seamless gutter system added around the perimeter of the home. Landscape/pathway lighting provide added security and curb appeal. Situated on a spacious 1/2 acre lot- no HOA! Zoned for Lowndes County Schools. Termite bonded (Astro), security system, sprinkler system, privacy fenced, and 2 car garage. Minutes from Publix, Aldi, SGMC, restaurants, and shopping. Seller is a licensed REALTOR in the state of GA.
